{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/sense-theme-zoom-slider-with-arrows","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1861,"date":"2022-10-26T08:56:00","date_gmt":"2022-10-26T08:56:00","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1861"},"modified":"2022-10-28T11:57:04","modified_gmt":"2022-10-28T11:57:04","slug":"sense-theme-zoom-slider-with-arrows","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/sense-theme-zoom-slider-with-arrows/","title":{"rendered":"Sense theme: click to zoom slider with arrows (mobile &#038; desktop)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The Sense theme is one of the most popular free themes available for use on Shopify, boasting a design that focuses on establishing trust between clients and store owners with soft but upbeat color pallets and plentiful product and brand information. That includes a zoom functionality that allows clients to see bigger versions of each product&#8217;s image. <br><br>While a very useful feature, it doesn&#8217;t work as well as it could for providing the smoothest experience for potential buyers interested in knowing more about your merchandise. This guide will teach you how to easily install a new zoom slider that not only fixes some kinks from the default feature, but also adds arrows for faster browsing with less scrolling, a design philosophy that works with the strengths of the Sense theme, making your clients feel better connected to your store brand through improved UX.<br><br>You can see it working in real time in our demo store: <a href=\"https://sense-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/ezfy-zoom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-code-files\">Downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can download the code files <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/sense-theme-zoom-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">clicking here</a>. (<a href=\"https://sense-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/ezfy-zoom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-finding-the-code\">Finding the code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Starting from your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1266\" height=\"464\" class=\"wp-image-1872\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-sense-1.png\" alt=\"Opening code editor from the shopify store admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-sense-1.png 1266w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-sense-1-850x312.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-sense-1-1200x440.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-sense-1-768x281.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1266px) 100vw, 1266px\" /><br></li><li>Within the <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/sense-theme-zoom-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">.zip you downloaded</a> is the following file: <br><strong>ezfy-zoom.txt</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-your-theme\">Adding the code to your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Copy all the code inside the <strong>ezfy-zoom.txt </strong>file.</li><li>Return to your Shopify code editor, find the <strong>Snippets</strong> folder click on &#8220;<em>Add a new snippet</em>&#8221; at the top. <br><br>Name it exactly: <strong>ezfy-zoom</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1401\" height=\"698\" class=\"wp-image-894\" style=\"width: 650px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1.png 1401w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-600x299.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-1200x598.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-768x383.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1401px) 100vw, 1401px\" /><br></li><li>Paste the code from before and click on <strong>save</strong>.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1564\" height=\"438\" class=\"wp-image-896\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2.jpg 1564w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-600x168.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-1200x336.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-768x215.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-1536x430.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1564px) 100vw, 1564px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Final step: activating the code in your store</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In the <strong>Layout</strong> folder open the file named <strong>theme.liquid</strong>.</li><li>In the file press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) to open the search bar, type in:<br><br><strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong></li><li><strong>Before&nbsp;</strong>the&nbsp;<strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong>&nbsp;tag you found paste the following code and then click on save:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-zoom' %}</code></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"720\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-898\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3.jpg 720w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3-600x582.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And you&#8217;re done! Click on the magnifying glass icon in any image from your product page and see the improved feature you just installed working in your store.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-1 wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"></div></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Make your clients more comfortable with improved zoom functionality for your Sense theme store, using only copy and paste code.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":1904,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[652],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-slider-3-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-slider-3-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-slider-3-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Sense Theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-slider-3.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1861"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/5"}],"r